data.description: Spacious home waiting for your finishing ideas. Enter to this open concept floor plan to newly refinished hardwood floors. Entryway is anchored by two rooms that make perfect sitting rooms or offices. First floor master suite with fireplace, and on suite spa like feel of its luxurious master bath with an AMAZING walk-in shower for two with 10 SPRAY Jets surrounding you! Separate Dining area has unique ceiling details. Large Oak kitchen with lots of cabinet and counter space including a separate vegetable sink. Slider lead out to the deck, large backyard with small pond and large 33-foot pool. Additional first floor room with full bath makes a perfect guest room. Mudroom off of garage with storage, washer and dryer area. Upstairs hosts two large bedrooms, and full bath. Along with another on-suite master bedroom. Large closets, two with custom closet organizers and expansive storage areas. Basement with newer carpet, living space and another full bathroom. Large windows throughout making this home bright and inviting. Connected garage with extra tall doors. 2 Story separate garage with high garage doors can hold that possible camper or boat. 2nd floor unfinished with lots of potential.
